====Pokémon Adventures====
{{main|Y (Adventures)}}
The character Yvonne Gabena, more commonly referred to as Y, is modeled after Serena. She is an aspiring {{tc|Sky Trainer}}, having chosen to become one to oppose people's expectations of her following in {{kal|Grace|her mother}}'s footsteps as a {{p|Rhyhorn}} racer. She rotates through several different hairstyles throughout the {{MangaArc|X & Y}}.
